IMPLEMENTATION STATUS
====================================================================================================

| Feature                    | Status      | Implementation Details                                                              |
|----------------------------|-------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| **Visual Changes**         |             |                                                                                     |
| Resize to 1080x1920        | ‚úÖ Done     | Resizes to 1080x1920 (9:16 vertical), pads if needed, sets SAR 1:1                   |
| Crop/zoom frame            | ‚úÖ Done     | Applies a 3% centre-crop (crop=iw*0.97:ih*0.97)                                     |
| Add overlay text           | ‚úÖ Done     | GUI: Per-video text, pos, size, color, bg-color, bold/italic styles                 |
| Tweak color settings       | ‚úÖ Done     | Slight brightness (0.005) & contrast (1.005) adjustments                            |
| Flip video horizontally    | ‚úÖ Done     | Optional via `--hflip` (CLI) or global GUI checkbox                                 |
| Change playback speed      | ‚ùå Not done | Video speed unchanged (audio pitch is shifted separately)                             |
| Add watermark/dot          | ‚úÖ Done     | Adds 2x2px white dot (top-left); GUI offers advanced text overlay (see above)       |
| Trim video duration        | ‚úÖ Done     | Trims video to a maximum of 29 seconds                                              |
| **Audio Changes**          |             |                                                                                     |
| Shift audio pitch          | ‚úÖ Done     | Pitch shifted up by ~3% (asetrate=SAMPLERATE*1.03, resamples)                      |
| Add background noise       | ‚úÖ Done     | Mixes `sounds/background_noise.mp3` if present, else auto-generates white noise     |
| Use TikTok voiceover       | ‚ùå Not done | Not implemented; would require TikTok app integration                               |
| Cut/offset audio           | ‚úÖ Done     | Adds 200ms delay to audio track (adelay=200|200)                                   |
| **Metadata Changes**       |             |                                                                                     |
| Remove metadata            | ‚úÖ Done     | Strips all metadata (`-map_metadata -1`)                                            |
| Re-export video            | ‚úÖ Done     | Fully re-encoded with libx264 (video) and aac (audio)                             |